      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented V&V history and version-controlled case files meets MRL 2 SQA requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used with institutional license tracking and version-controlled simulation input files stored in a Git repository. Release notes and solver validation documentation confirm compliance with MRL 2 SQA expectations."
