      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver benchmark problems for rotating-frame incompressible flow demonstrate correct numerical implementation.",
      "rationale": "Standard lid-driven cavity and rotating channel benchmark cases were executed and compared against published analytical solutions. Residual norms converged to below 1e-6 and velocity errors were within 0.5% of reference values, confirming correct solver implementation for the relevant flow regime."
