      "rationale": "Three structured hexahedral meshes (2.1M, 5.4M, and 11.8M cells) were evaluated. Richardson extrapolation yielded a GCI of 1.8% for the hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point (3 LPM, 3500 RPM), exceeding the required level and confirming mesh-adequate discretization."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
